Subject: Re: [VB] alternator help

Yes without power from your "dummy light" wire the
alternator will not charge.  Try putting your oil
light into the charging light socket, and it should
start charging.  Or use one of the dash light bulbs. 
Bulbs are available from almost any type 2 or type
three or your local FLVWAPS.

